'''G & G vs. Wikimedia Foundation, Inc.''' [2009] [[EWHC]] 3148 (QB) was an English legal case. The case involved "G" who sought a [[Norwich Pharmacal order]] requiring that the respondent disclose the [[IP address]] of an individual who had edited Wikipedia to include private and sensitive information about her and her child.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.5rb.com/case/g-g-v-wikimedia-foundation-inc/ |title=G & G v Wikimedia Foundation Inc |publisher=5RB |date=2009-12-02 |accessdate=2016-07-16}}</ref> The order was granted.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.onebrickcourt.com/cases.aspx?menu=main&pageid=42&caseid=249 |title=Cases - G and G v Wikimedia Foundation Inc [2009&#93; EWHC 3148 (QB) |publisher=One Brick Court |date= |accessdate=2016-07-16}}</ref>

